{"tid":332222,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"歷代火影邊個最偉大？","createTime":"2017-07-22T21:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T07:52:57.000Z","uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a11a52014cfdce488caea1ef13a1e209b5685d0","tid":332222,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:48:09.000Z","msg":"我相信好多人都會覺得係第一代<br />\n佢建立起木葉 制止左班 封印左九尾 幾乎係歷代最強火影<br />\n<br />\n但係我眼中 無人及得上波風水門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣對付住九尾 佢實力可以話差一代成大截 但佢堅持火影嘅職責 甚麼犧牲自己 都要封印九尾<br />\n<br />\n攞起戰衣 就要踏上不歸路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/054319_5a57ea95326a6989abd1ce0e1040debc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F054319_5a57ea95326a6989abd1ce0e1040debc.jpg&h=c4ff0a37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3abad3342edd735fa2a0f4b19cc2c0216e4bcfb","tid":332222,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:48:49.000Z","msg":"錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148328024fba2e20a3a80cf329a1e4489122dfa8","tid":332222,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:50:27.000Z","msg":"都係一、四啦<br />\n二都ok... 幫一代執屎<br />\n鳴仔更加唔使講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c32c50b0d4aa518a67aa3438c32ba57fe501cb","tid":332222,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T22:04:49.000Z","msg":"三代啦<br />\n話曬都有分身手裏劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c87ad28e8a8ae8e747f67ccb9a648c72f65637b","tid":332222,"uid":130084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T22:06:40.000Z","msg":"四代"},{"pid":"0be28c697d4abc99a59dd995b601079d3d1e8da9","tid":332222,"uid":130084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0